Marketing Research
TogetherDating( Niche Dating App)
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Our objective: We are aiming to make a product that attract potentials partners for intentional matchmaking for adventures. 

Target Audience: Our audience are niche focused on those who enjoy outdoor adventures from hiking to skiing. Adapt to User Profiles and Interest*
Right now the biggest target audience group of dating apps comprises 25-34 year olds
 

Our vision: This team project aims to build an outdoor app for adventure seekers and provide all online users seamless access to an experience-driven platform that allows them to connect to a community of outdoor enthusiasts and find a match on criteria simply beyond location.
Types of Dating Apps 

Top competitors:
https://www.datingadvice.com/online-dating/outdoor-dating-site
Here there are 13 other “outdoors” dating sites that fit into our niche. We can should analysis their tactics used to attract and hold a certain type of audience.

Feature analysis: According to (cometchat, 2022) there are quite a few features that every dating app should incorporate. 
1.	Gamified User Profiles
2.	In-app chat and messaging 
3.	Ice breakers(What is your spirit location?)
4.	Voice and Video chatting
5.	Smart Push Notifications
6.	In app Games
7.	Social Media Integration.
*We should not aim to have exactly every feature however we should aim to plan to have it integrated in future updates.

Additional Features:
1.	Security : This includes platform security and User security. Both are instrumental to the development of the application
2.	Matching: Types of matching
Geolocation
AI 
Behavior – based 
Compatibility
Matching Limit(Moderation)
https://sloboda-studio.com/blog/how-to-create-a-dating-app/
Helpful Information: 
Revenue Peek to hit $2.5 billion in 2024
•	Revenue in the online dating segment is expected to amount to US$2.5 billion in 2024.
 
•	Most revenue in online dating is generated in the United States ($259.3 million in 2024).
 



 
